    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>sushi rice </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 25 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>sticky rice</strong></p>",
