    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, cut the <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong> to a bowl with<strong> </strong>the <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong> and the <strong>remaining gochujang paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> gochujang cucumber</strong></p>",
